    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Berserker
    An extension of the Hero class for the Berserker role
    Healer
    An extension of the Hero class for the Healer role
    Hero
    The Hero abstract class, used to create different types of hero
    Heroes
    Public data about all the heroes including the roles and unique names based on team and role type.
    Heroes.Role
    The three kinds of heroes
    HeroParty
    HeroParty is an implementation of Party that tracks 3 heroes on the same team
    HeroStorm
    The HeroStorm class controls the main operation of the program and includes the main method
    Party
    An interface used as a blueprint for Party
    Tank
    An extension of the Hero class for the Tank role
    Team
    Public enum representing the two teams
    TestBerserker
    A test class for the beserkers.
    TestHealer
    A test class for the healers.
    TestParty
    This is a party used only for testing.
    TestTank
